<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Question Has Been Answered - EduMaroc</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;600&display=swap');
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7f9;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 16px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -20px;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 50% 100%);
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
            color: #333333;
        }
        .content p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f0f7ff;
            border-left: 4px solid #4a90e2;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .highlight-box h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #4a90e2;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4a90e2;
            color: #ffffff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #3a7bc8;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f0f7ff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666666;
        }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 20px;
            }
            .header {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your Question Has Been Answered!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= name %>,</p>
            <p>Great news! Your question about the course "<%= title %>" has been answered by one of our expert instructors. We're excited for you to continue your learning journey with this new insight.</p>
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <h2>What's Next?</h2>
                <p>1. Review the answer to your question</p>
                <p>2. Continue with your course material</p>
                <p>3. Engage in discussions with fellow learners</p>
            </div>
            <p>Remember, asking questions is a crucial part of the learning process. We encourage you to keep exploring and inquiring as you progress through your courses on EduMaroc.</p>
            <p>If you have any more questions or need further clarification, don't hesitate to reach out. Our instructors and support team are here to help you succeed.</p>
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="https://edumaroc.com/my-courses" class="button">Go to My Courses</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 EduMaroc. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>123 Education Street, Casablanca, Morocco</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>